snippet.title: Project F4E Playtest - Join Wolfswood
snippet.description:
Project F4E is a Hardcore Fantasy Extraction ARPG game. Embark in a PvEvP experience where you and your team venture on missions to complete objectives and get loot before extracting. Will you be able to survive?
-------------------
Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/306910/Project_F4E/ 

Join us on X: https://x.com/betadwarf
